      "message": "kHardLineBreakBefore\n\nThe ICU iterators return the index of the fenceposts, so 0 means \u0027before position 0\u0027. I think this important because kWhiteSpace is a property of the codepoints. Mixing these two can be confusing, so it seems easier to name them all as applying to the fText, even if it can be one longer than fText.",
